Class Notification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.resourcemanager.model.Notification

    @Entity(name="Notification")
public class Notification
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Notification data model. Represents a message for a user, created on a specific date and time, and whether or not it has been seen or not.
